<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong Correctional Services
Department carried out an operation this morning to clear Section
Two of the Whitehead Detention Center (WHDC) in preparation for
closing the center before 1997.
</P>
<P>
An official release said that 462 Vietnamese migrants (VMs)
were smoothly transferred to High Island Detention Center (HIDC)
during the operation.
</P>
<P>
