Over the past two days, some 800 VMs in Section Two volunteered
to come forward and were transported to HIDC. 210 VMs were
transferred to other sections in WHDC and 35 joined the Voluntary
Repatriation Program.
</P>
<P>
A spokesman said today's operation was carried out without
incident. But a few VMs had to be physically removed from the
section as they refused to co-operate.  
