Diplomats from these countries and officials from the State
Nationalities Affairs Commission, Central University of
Nationalities and Chinese Buddhist Association took part in the
festive event.
</P>
<P>
Artists from the Dai, Va and Yi ethnic groups performed dances
and songs, and played various games. 
