jointly launched the services of "Newsline" and "RTHK Radio One
Line."
</P>
<P>
Just by dialing the number 900-0038-7199, local callers can
have a free access to the latest news programs updated each hour.
On the other line, numbered 900-0038-7188, all programs of the
RTHK Radio One are offered.
</P>
<P>
Overseas callers are able to keep in pace with what is going on
in Hong Kong by paying IDD rates for the services.
</P>
<P>
