<HEADLINE> U.S. Planes Arrive in Jordan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Thirty-four American jet fighters
and transport planes arrived in Jordan Friday for training
exercises with the Jordanian air force and for carrying out
surveillance flights over southern Iraq.
</P>
<P>
