flights are 18 F-16s, 12 F-15s and 4 KC-135 tanker jets,
according to the daily Jordan Times today.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. planes landed at a military air base, north of Amman,
and the code-named "Eager Tiger" joint exercises are expected to
start on Monday, officials here said.
</P>
