unethical banking practices like insider lending, poor appraisal
of loans and poor loan recovery that "are the main problems of
banks in Uganda today."
</P>
<P>
In his speech, Mahemdra Mehta, chairman of the bank, said
because the bank has a background in the agricultural sector, it
will strive to find ways on how to help that sector grow. 
</P>
