Southeast Asia, the Tourism Authority of Thailand (TAT) said
today.
</P>
<P>
According to a TAT press release, Thailand has made ample
preparations for the PATA meetings, including the 45th annual
conference scheduled for April 21-25 in Bangkok and to be attended
by over 1,000 delegates.
</P>
<P>
