dollars) for the arrangements of the meetings and tourism
promotion activities.
</P>
<P>
The number of tourist arrivals in Thailand and the country's
tourism revenues have been rising steadily over the past years.
</P>
<P>
The government set a target of attracting 7.2 million tourist
arrivals and reaping revenues worth around 8 billion US dollars
this year. 
