</P>
<P>
The Pakistan Times
</P>
<P>
-- Tamil Tiger guerrillas carried out a Kamikaze-style attack
on Sri Lanka's main sea port Friday shortly after the military
cleared three Israeli-built jets that will be used against the
rebels.  
